reviewText:
i bought the dvd so i can show it to my friends when they come by to my house. i'm a man of science & i appreciated the way it was presented in this video that there's no opposition between religion & science;

  science will answer the how's & GOD will explain the "why's" !!!!

1 star less for no "close caption"  & other "menu"; just like watching a VHS on a DVD format.
